projects.title: Space Planning
projects.description: Graphic study showing arrangement of spaces, room layouts, and activities making up a floor plan.

projects.title: Site Planning
projects.description: Development of site plan options showing boundary lines, potential development boundaries, building location(s).

projects.title: Construction Planning
projects.description: The developer may want to establish a project budget in the Pre-Design Architecture phase.

projects.title: Bidding Planning
projects.description: At this time the owner prepares to select the contractor for the job and sign contracts to proceed with construction.

projects.title: Acception Planning
projects.description: The architect will be available to answer questions and provide additional information to issues that arise.
